{
  "stem": "14463.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 560.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, there was a corner there where he was assassinated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a restaurant there, you know, next door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and I had a cousin in there, which I met here in Australia later on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so life was quite pleasant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the thing which I remember about Lwow most is I had a bar mitzvah there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and of course, I didn't have to get ready for the bar mitzvah, because from cheder you ought not to-- there wasn't a Bible.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Whatever-- whatever parchment there was, I could read.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It didn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not like you have to get ready for the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A year ahead, [LAUGHS] I knew it, you know, straight away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I opened it up, and I could read it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little synagogue, and my uncle took me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what I remember about my brother's bar mitzvah, of course, was that my mother got sick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the doctor came, and she couldn't go with me to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he examined her, and he said Frau Weinreich, there's absolutely nothing wrong with you physically.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing which is wrong with you is you've got a broken heart, because my father wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to the-- to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that little synagogue very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was standing up at the top, and I was reciting my little piece.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went downstairs and everybody congratulated me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went home-- there was nothing to eat, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then a cousin came to rescue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was working at restaurant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He brought some food, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is what I remember about Lwow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My bar mitzvah there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when my son had a bar mitzvah here, I said I'm having my bar mitzvah together with you.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
